'''Steve James''' is an American film producer and director of several documentaries, including the award-winning ''[[Hoop Dreams]]'', and ''[[Stevie (film)|Stevie]]''.  He is a graduate of [[Southern Illinois University Carbondale]].  He is a long-time associate of [[Kartemquin Films]].

