==Filmography==

*''At the Death House Door'', in 2008 (filming) 
*''Reel Paradise'', in 2005 
*''"Independent Lens, 1 episode, The New Americans'', in 2004, TV Episode (Nigerian story director) 
*''Stevie'', in 2002 
*''Joe and Max,  ... aka Joe and Max - Rivalen im Ring (Germany)'', in 2002 (TV)
*''Passing Glory'', in 1999 (TV) 
*''Prefontaine'', in 1997 
*''Hoop Dreams'', in 1994 
*''Higher Goals'', in 1993
*''Grassroots Chicago'', in 1991
*''Stop Substance Abuse'', in 1986
